DataList.LocalizeJP: 戦闘ね？了解。
DataList.LocalizeEN: To battle? Understood.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 準備ならもうできてる。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Preparations are complete here.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 何？どうすればいい？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Hm? What should I do now?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 油断した。戻ったら反省会ね、先生。
DataList.LocalizeEN: We let our guard down. We'll have a meeting about this when we're back, Sensei.

DataList.LocalizeJP: しくじった…。次は、必ず。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I messed up... Next time, definitely.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 面倒だけど、これもトレーニングの一環。
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's a bother, but this also part of training.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 先生、指示をお願い。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Sensei, your orders.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 先生の指示もあったんだから、これくらいの勝利は当然。
DataList.LocalizeEN: We had Sensei on our side. It's only natural we find our victory.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 作戦成功。…でも少し簡単すぎ。トレーニングにしては物足りない。
DataList.LocalizeEN: The operation was a success. It was a bit too easy to serve as training.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ありがとう。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Thank you.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 準備完了。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Preparations complete.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 遮蔽物を確保。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Secure cover.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ハァ、まったく…！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Oh please.

DataList.LocalizeJP: これぐらい。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Is that all?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 無駄！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Pointless.

DataList.LocalizeJP: これより夏合宿のトレーニングを始める。
DataList.LocalizeEN: The summer camp training starts now.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 総員、遅れないように。行こう。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Everybody, do not stay behind. Let's go.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 暑い…めんどくさい！
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's hot and annoying.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ああ…まだいるの？
DataList.LocalizeEN: There are still more of you?

DataList.LocalizeJP: ありがとう。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Thank you.

DataList.LocalizeJP: あっ…熱中症…？ごめん…先生。
DataList.LocalizeEN: What? Heatstroke...? I'm sorry... Sensei.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 逃さない。
DataList.LocalizeEN: You won't get away.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 移動する。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Moving ahead.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 作戦成功。その…、あんまりじっと見ないでほしい。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Operation success. Ummm... don't stare at me so much.

DataList.LocalizeJP: これくらいたいした事じゃない。…だから、そんなにこっち見ないで！
DataList.LocalizeEN: This wasn't a big deal... so stop looking at me like that!

DataList.LocalizeJP: そこ！
DataList.LocalizeEN: There!

DataList.LocalizeJP: この海の風紀も私が守らないと！
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's up to me to maintain discipline on the beach!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 仕方ない…実力行使で！
DataList.LocalizeEN: It can't be helped... it'll be done by force!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 私がやらないと…か。
DataList.LocalizeEN: So it's up to me...

DataList.LocalizeJP: そろそろ諦めたら？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Would you give up already?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 逃さない。
DataList.LocalizeEN: You won't escape.

DataList.LocalizeJP: トレーニングとはいえ、容赦はしない。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Training or not, I'll show no mercy.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ちゃんと合宿の効果があったみたい。
DataList.LocalizeEN: It seems that the training camp had results after all.

DataList.LocalizeJP: こんな格好だけど…、私の助けが必要なら、いつでも言って？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Call me whenever you need my help, even if I'm wearing this...

DataList.LocalizeJP: 私はまだまだ強くなれる。先生のためにも強くなりたい。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I can still be stronger. I want to be stronger for Sensei.

DataList.LocalizeJP: いつもありがとう…。こんな私だけど…もう少し頼ってくれるとうれしい。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Thanks as always. You know I'd be glad if you relied on me a little more...

DataList.LocalizeJP: 今年の夏も先生と一緒にいられるんだね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: It looks like I'm spending another summer with Sensei.

DataList.LocalizeJP: せっかくの夏なのに…私みたいなつまらない子と一緒でいいの？私と…いっしょがいい？そ…そう。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Are you really fine spending time with a boring kid like me, even though it's summer? You... want to spend it with me?! I... I see.

DataList.LocalizeJP: あ、あんまりくっつかないで！いくら私でもその…。この格好だと、さすがに恥ずかしい…！
DataList.LocalizeEN: C-could you move away a little! I know it's just us but... it's a little embarrassing, dressed like this.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 先生の手、ひんやりしてて気持ちいい。外はこんなに日が照ってるし、その…もう少し。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Sensei's hands are cool and comfortable. It's so sunny outside and, can I... just a little longer?
